basic.blooming: Flowering period May, fruiting period June

maintenance.soil: Soil with loose texture or special humus soil, pH value 6-7
maintenance.sunlight: Like sunshine, grows in sunny places
maintenance.watering: Like water, water thoroughly after soil surface dries, avoid saturated water
maintenance.fertilization: Enjoy much fertilizer, apply fertilizer during growing time
